State of Connecticut v. Dale Brooks (6948)

Borden, Daly and Norcott, Js.

Argued November 8 decision released November 14, 1989 Charles C. Greenwald, for the appellant (defendant). Leah Hawley, assistant state’s attorney, with whom, on the brief, were C. Robert Satti, Sr., state’s attorney, and Michael Regan, assistant state’s attorney, for the appellee (state). Per Curiam.

There is no error.
